  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>An elegant wing-assisted jetpack, inspired by the design philosophy of exotic starships. This exclusive exosuit augmentation commemorates completion of the 'Exobiology' <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Expedition</span>.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">装置套装外观</span>。<br><br>造型优雅的飞翼型喷气背包，灵感来源于异星飞船的奇异设计理念。这款专属的套装外观纪念了你完成“异星生物学”<span class=\"name name-stellar\">远征</span>。<br><br>可以在外观修改器使用以更改你的<span class=\"name name-technology\">套装外观</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>一款優雅的機翼輔助噴射背包，靈感來自外星太空船的設計理念。這個特殊的強化套裝擴充是完成「外星生物學」<span class=\"name name-stellar\">探險</span>的紀念。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>裡改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
  },
